results.name: Number of non-isomorphic multiset partitions with no singletons of aperiodic multisets of size n.
comment: Also the number of nonnegative integer matrices up to row and column permutations with sum of elements equal to n and no zero rows or columns, in which (1) the row sums are all > 1 and (2) the column sums are relatively prime.
A multiset is aperiodic if its multiplicities are relatively prime.
The weight of a multiset partition is the sum of sizes of its parts. Weight is generally not the same as number of vertices.
